主厨" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img1.wsyzy.org/upload/vod/20260605-1/b0dab60379a25a8d4b2c2b16299987ee.jpg" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="型男大主厨"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2006</span><span class="video-class">综艺</span><span>台湾</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/803.html" title="型男大主厨">型男大主厨</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9B%BE%E5%9B%BD%E5%9F%8E.html" target="_blank">曾国城</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%99%88%E4%B9%94%E6%81%A9.html" target="_blank">陈乔恩</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%A4%8F%E4%BA%8E%E4%B9%94.html" target="_blank">夏于乔</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%98%BF%E5%9F%BA%E5%B8%88.html" target="_blank">阿基师</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%83%91%E5%9D%9A%E5%85%8B.html" target="_blank">郑坚克</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%AE%B7%E7%90%A6.html" target="_blank">殷琦</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">《型男大主厨》自2006年7月10日首播推出以来，收视率长期占据台湾美食教学类节目收视第一名的位置，内容综合烹饪节目性质及综艺竞赛型态，也成为艺人宣传作品必上的一个节目。</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/803.html" class="module-item-title" title="型男大主厨">型男大主厨</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至20260611期</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/139313.html" title="创业面对面" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://vcover-vt-pic.puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/mzc002006kj7vng1777539253197/0" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="创业面对面"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">综艺</span><span>内地</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/139313.html" title="创业面对面">创业面对面</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">《创业面对面》作为《非你莫属》升级版，每期邀请不同的创业者跟大家一起分享他们遇到的那些人和事儿，讲述他们的职场故事。</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/139313.html" class="module-item-title" title="创业面对面">创业面对面</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至20260608期</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/802.html" title="人气美食" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img1.wsyzy.org/upload/vod/20260605-1/9d15efc6ee903195ac7aa38c2fb57a32.jpg" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="人气美食"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2007</span><span class="video-class">综艺</span><span>中国大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/802.html" title="人气美食">人气美食</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%98%BF%E6%A5%A0.html" target="_blank">阿楠</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B4%8B%E5%AD%90.html" target="_blank">洋子</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%B7%AF%E6%98%93.html" target="_blank">路易</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%AB%8B%E9%9D%92.html" target="_blank">立青</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B0%8F%E7%BE%8E.html" target="_blank">小美</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">开办于2007年的《人气美食》为美食榜单、人气小店、民间美食、烹饪厨艺和饮食风俗为主要内容的美食文化节目。《人气美食》为星尚传媒著名的三大资讯节目之一，现在已成为上海美食最权威的指南。　　《人气美</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/802.html" class="module-item-title" title="人气美食">人气美食</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新202606010</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/11742.html" title="最优秀山" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260505-1/1af5966b8610c28ce740a5226a28acaf.jpg" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="最优秀山"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">综艺</span><span>韩国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/11742.html" title="最优秀山">最优秀山</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%9C%E6%B0%91.html" target="_blank">张东民</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%BF%9E%E4%B8%96%E6%B6%A6.html" target="_blank">俞世润</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%A2%81%E4%B8%96%E7%82%AF.html" target="_blank">梁世炯</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%AE%B8%E5%8D%BF%E7%84%95.html" target="_blank">许卿焕</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Boom.html" target="_blank">Boom</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">简介：首档山间综艺，规则只有一个，完成山路上展开的任务，收集“橡实”！考验集谈话、体力、感性于一身的公认六边形最优秀综艺人的能力！山间展开的不可预测、跌跌撞撞的任务游行！只有拥有最多橡实的一个人才能登上最优秀者的宝座！向着最终任务舞台“山顶”前进，这是世界上最无用、最激烈的山顶争夺战</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/11742.html" class="module-item-title" title="最优秀山">最优秀山</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至05期</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-