ndex.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B2%A9%E8%B0%B7%E5%81%A5%E5%8F%B8.html" target="_blank">岩谷健司</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　本作是以东京都内某栋独户住宅为舞台的&amp;quot;纯粹社会派深刻喜剧&amp;quot;。曜子在丈夫工作期间，既在一楼照料公公，又在二楼经营非法风俗店。对政治与社会保持敏感、同时竭力兼顾看护工作与风俗营业的曜</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/165431.html" class="module-item-title" title="亚洲的独特国度">亚洲的独特国度</a></div><div class="module-item-text">正片</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/163640.html" title="种墨园" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.lzipic.com/upload/vod/20260623-1/2ea35c97bb92e4d2cd5d0bd0cbedbdb6.webp" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="种墨园"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">剧集</span><span>中国大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/163640.html" title="种墨园">种墨园</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%83%91%E4%B8%9A%E6%88%90.html" target="_blank">郑业成</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%BC%A0%E6%9C%88.html" target="_blank">张月</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%A9%AC%E5%B0%91%E9%AA%85.html" target="_blank">马少骅</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%8E%8B%E8%8C%9C%E5%8D%8E.html" target="_blank">王茜华</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%83%A1%E8%80%98%E8%B1%AA.html" target="_blank">胡耘豪</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%86%8A%E7%9D%BF%E7%8E%B2.html" target="_blank">熊睿玲</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%BD%90%E5%8D%83%E9%83%A1.html" target="_blank">齐千郡</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%8F%E5%A4%A9.html" target="_blank">印小天</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%AE%8B%E7%A6%B9.html" target="_blank">宋禹</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%91%9B%E5%AD%90.html" target="_blank">瑛子</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%8E%8B%E5%8A%B2%E6%9D%BE.html" target="_blank">王劲松</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%B8%81%E5%8B%87%E5%B2%B1.html" target="_blank">丁勇岱</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%90%B4%E5%85%B6%E6%B1%9F.html" target="_blank">吴其江</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%90%B4%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%89.html" target="_blank">吴京安</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">在北京工作的林依然，因母亲患病，选择回乡后考公到桃花镇，在经发办任职。林依然看到以千年宣家为代表的传统宣纸产业艰难求存，为了拯救传统宣纸产业，她通过开发宣纸笔记本业务、去北京拉宣纸壁纸订单、操办文房四</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/163640.html" class="module-item-title" title="种墨园">种墨园</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至第01集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/165414.html" title="世界在起舞" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2026-06-29/202606291782741308.jpg" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="世界在起舞"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">动漫</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/165414.html" title="世界在起舞">世界在起舞</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%8A%B1%E5%AE%88%E7%94%B1%E7%BE%8E%E9%87%8C.html" target="_blank">花守由美里</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%9C%9F%E5%B1%8B%E7%A5%9E%E5%8F%B6.html" target="_blank">土屋神叶</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%86%85%E7%94%B0%E7%9C%9F%E7%A4%BC.html" target="_blank">内田真礼</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%B4%E7%92%90%E7%BE%8E.html" target="_blank">朴璐美</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%A8%B1%E4%BA%95%E5%AD%9D%E5%AE%8F.html" target="_blank">樱井孝宏</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Takahiro.html" target="_blank">Takahiro</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Sakurai.html" target="_blank">Sakurai</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B0%8F%E8%A5%BF%E5%85%8B%E5%B9%B8.html" target="_blank">小西克幸</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Katsuyuki.html" target="_blank">Katsuyuki</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Konishi.html" target="_blank">Konishi</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%A3%9E%E7%94%B0%E5%B1%95%E7%94%B7.html" target="_blank">飞田展男</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%83%BD%E7%99%BB%E9%BA%BB%E7%BE%8E%E5%AD%90.html" target="_blank">能登麻美子</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Mamiko.html" target="_blank">Mamiko</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Noto.html" target="_blank">Noto</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B0%B4%E6%BF%91%E7%A5%88.html" target="_blank">水濑祈</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Inori.html" target="_blank">Inori</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Minase.html" target="_blank">Minase</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%9F%B3%E8%B0%B7%E6%98%A5%E8%B4%B5.html" target="_blank">石谷春贵</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%80%AC%E6%88%B8%E8%8A%AD%E6%9C%88.html" target="_blank">瀬戸芭月</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　以室町时代为舞台，讲述了后来被称为世阿弥的美少年“鬼夜叉”的故事。在一切以技艺为重的父亲观阿弥身边长大，鬼夜叉始终无法理解人类为何会享受艺术与表演。某一天，他在村子边缘的一户民宅中，看见一名唱歌跳</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/165414.html" class="module-item-title" title="世界在起舞">世界在起舞</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至00集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/12439.html" title="所爱之人" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260410-1/aef0e981efc900e74dd978677c107b64.webp" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="所爱之人"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">剧集</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/12439.html" title="所爱之人">所爱之人</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%97%A4%E5%86%88%E9%9D%9B.html" target="_blank">藤冈靛</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B3%B7%E5%86%85%E5%85%AC%E7%BE%8E.html" target="_blank">泷内公美</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%85%AB%E6%9C%A8%E5%8B%87%E5%BE%81.html" target="_blank">八木勇征</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%BA%B2%E5%90%AF%E6%B0%B8.html" target="_blank">纲启永</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%AE%89%E9%BD%90%E6%98%9F%E6%9D%A5.html" target="_blank">安齐星来</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B7%9D%E5%BA%8A%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E9%A6%99.html" target="_blank">川床明日香</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%8D%89%E5%B7%9D%E6%8B%93%E5%BC%A5.html" target="_blank">草川拓弥</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B1%B1%E5%8F%A3%E7%BA%B1%E5%BC%A5%E5%8A%A0.html" target="_blank">山口纱弥加</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%B8%8A%E5%B7%9D%E6%8B%93%E9%83%8E.html" target="_blank">上川拓郎</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B0%8F%E6%9D%BE%E5%92%8C%E9%87%8D.html" target="_blank">小松和重</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">日本每年有约20万具遗体被归为“死因不明”，真正接受法医学解剖的不足一成。为改变这一现状，厚生劳动省主导成立了拥有调查指示与解剖决定权的法医学专业团队——MEJ（Medical Examiner Japan）。 从美国归来的天才法医学者水泽真澄（藤冈靛 饰）曾参与大量检死工作。他性格独特却洞察敏锐，不被常识束缚，常以一句“这存在矛盾”追问真相。面对遗体时，他以“LOVED ONE”相称，从细微痕迹中还原逝者生前的时间与被掩盖的事实。 与他搭档的是MEJ中心长桐生麻帆（泷内公美 饰）。出身母子家庭的她立志通</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/12439.html" class="module-item-title" title="所爱之人">所爱之人</a></div><div class="module-item-text">第7集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/713.html" title="冰之城墙" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.jisuimage.com/cover/1b0535497c445db5a242f72edb9cdc52.jpg" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="冰之城墙"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">动漫</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/713.html" title="冰之城墙">冰之城墙</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B0%B8%E6%BF%91%E5%AE%89%E5%A5%88.html" target="_blank">永濑安奈</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%92%8C%E6%B3%89%E9%A3%8E%E8%8A%B1.html" target="_blank">和泉风花</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%8D%83%E5%8F%B6%E7%BF%94%E4%B9%9F.html" target="_blank">千叶翔也</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%8C%AA%E8%82%A1%E6%85%A7%E5%A3%AB.html" target="_blank">猪股慧士</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%96%B0%E7%A6%8F%E6%A8%B1.html" target="_blank">新福樱</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B0%8F%E6%9E%97%E5%8D%83%E6%99%83.html" target="_blank">小林千晃</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%AC%BC%E5%A4%B4%E6%98%8E%E9%87%8C.html" target="_blank">鬼头明里</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B3%A2%E5%A4%9A%E9%87%8E%E7%BF%94.html" target="_blank">波多野翔</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B7%9D%E4%BA%95%E7%94%B0%E5%A4%8F%E6%B5%B7.html" target="_blank">川井田夏海</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">冰川小雪是一位内向的学生，她总是向外筑起一道高高的心墙，只跟儿时好友安昙美姫互动。有一天，名叫雨宫凑的男孩，没来由地开始试图打进小雪的心房，扰乱了她平静的生活。</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/713.html" class="module-item-title" title="冰之城墙">冰之城墙</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新第11集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/11407.html" title="医到孤岛爱上你" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260601-1/a55bd04b0530835e782b572390bdff06.webp" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="医到孤岛爱上你"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">剧集</span><span>韩国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/11407.html" title="医到孤岛爱上你">医到孤岛爱上你</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B0%E6%97%AD.html" target="_blank">李宰旭</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%BE%9B%E7%9D%BF%E6%81%A9.html" target="_blank">辛睿恩</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%91%E5%9F%BA.html" target="_blank">洪民基</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A7%80%E6%95%AC.html" target="_blank">李秀敬</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">立志成为顶尖整形外科医生都志义（李宰旭 饰），同身世神秘的助理护士陆遐俐（辛叡恩 饰），在命运安排下被分配到与世隔绝、恶名昭彰的“平同岛”上工作。两个同样受伤的灵魂，在艰难环境中共同成长，展开彼此疗愈的浪漫故事。 该剧改编自同名漫画。</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/11407.html" class="module-item-title" title="医到孤岛爱上你">医到孤岛爱上你</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至第04集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="