href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/163640.html" class="module-item-title" title="种墨园">种墨园</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至第01集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/12439.html" title="所爱之人" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260410-1/aef0e981efc900e74dd978677c107b64.webp" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="所爱之人"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">剧集</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/12439.html" title="所爱之人">所爱之人</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%97%A4%E5%86%88%E9%9D%9B.html" target="_blank">藤冈靛</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B3%B7%E5%86%85%E5%85%AC%E7%BE%8E.html" target="_blank">泷内公美</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%85%AB%E6%9C%A8%E5%8B%87%E5%BE%81.html" target="_blank">八木勇征</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%BA%B2%E5%90%AF%E6%B0%B8.html" target="_blank">纲启永</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%AE%89%E9%BD%90%E6%98%9F%E6%9D%A5.html" target="_blank">安齐星来</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B7%9D%E5%BA%8A%E6%98%8E%E6%97%A5%E9%A6%99.html" target="_blank">川床明日香</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%8D%89%E5%B7%9D%E6%8B%93%E5%BC%A5.html" target="_blank">草川拓弥</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B1%B1%E5%8F%A3%E7%BA%B1%E5%BC%A5%E5%8A%A0.html" target="_blank">山口纱弥加</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%B8%8A%E5%B7%9D%E6%8B%93%E9%83%8E.html" target="_blank">上川拓郎</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B0%8F%E6%9D%BE%E5%92%8C%E9%87%8D.html" target="_blank">小松和重</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">日本每年有约20万具遗体被归为“死因不明”，真正接受法医学解剖的不足一成。为改变这一现状，厚生劳动省主导成立了拥有调查指示与解剖决定权的法医学专业团队——MEJ（Medical Examiner Japan）。 从美国归来的天才法医学者水泽真澄（藤冈靛 饰）曾参与大量检死工作。他性格独特却洞察敏锐，不被常识束缚，常以一句“这存在矛盾”追问真相。面对遗体时，他以“LOVED ONE”相称，从细微痕迹中还原逝者生前的时间与被掩盖的事实。 与他搭档的是MEJ中心长桐生麻帆（泷内公美 饰）。出身母子家庭的她立志通</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/12439.html" class="module-item-title" title="所爱之人">所爱之人</a></div><div class="module-item-text">第7集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/11407.html" title="医到孤岛爱上你" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260601-1/a55bd04b0530835e782b572390bdff06.webp" src="https://img.yixin.ai/yixinimg/sitepic/mzload.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="医到孤岛爱上你"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">剧集</span><span>韩国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/11407.html" title="医到孤岛爱上你">医到孤岛爱上你</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B0%E6%97%AD.html" target="_blank">李宰旭</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%BE%9B%E7%9D%BF%E6%81%A9.html" target="_blank">辛睿恩</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B4%AA%E6%B0%91%E5%9F%BA.html" target="_blank">洪民基</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A7%80%E6%95%AC.html" target="_blank">李秀敬</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">立志成为顶尖整形外科医生都志义（李宰旭 饰），同身世神秘的助理护士陆遐俐（辛叡恩 饰），在命运安排下被分配到与世隔绝、恶名昭彰的“平同岛”上工作。两个同样受伤的灵魂，在艰难环境中共同成长，展开彼此疗愈的浪漫故事。 该剧改编自同名漫画。</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/detail/id/11407.html" class="module-item-title" title="医到孤岛爱上你">医到孤岛爱上你<